# Place your game assets here

## Required GIF files:
- player.gif (Your main character - displayed as rounded circle)
- powerup.gif (Power-up character - displayed as rounded circle)

## Optional Audio files:
- background-music.mp3 (Plays during gameplay, loops continuously)
- game-over.mp3 (Plays when character dies)
- powerup.mp3 (Plays when collecting powerup stars for extra points)

The game will work without audio files, but they enhance the experience!

Trees 🌳 and cockroaches 🪳 use emojis (no GIF needed).
